Global Porokeratosis Treatment Market Insights
Porokeratosis Treatment Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Porokeratosis Treatment Market Overview
The global porokeratosis treatment market is anticipated to witness significant growth over the forecast period, driven by the increasing incidence of porokeratosis-related skin disorders and the growing awareness about skin health. The market is expected to reach USD 300 million by 2028, expanding at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2023. Factors such as the development of novel therapies, rising demand for effective treatments, and the availability of advanced healthcare systems in developed regions will further enhance market prospects. The adoption of both topical and systemic treatments is rising, as more patients seek relief from the condition's symptoms.

